Frequently Asked Questions:

🦁 Who are you? What is this?
My name is Ari Horesh. I am 22. I am a medical student from Italy (University of Pavia), and in the past couple of years, I dedicated my time and money to educate people worldwide.

I have a non-profit project, called "EnterMedSchool" - Where I helped over 12,000 medical aspirants to take the medical admission exam, absolutely free.
I am passionate about bringing people together and encouraging them to strive to know more.

I truly believe knowledge should be free. I want to help future medical (but not only) students to reach their goals and dreams as well. 
Feel free to ask me more about it during the breaks!

🦁 How often do you live stream? 6-7 times a week. 12 hours each time.
🦁 What do you study? I study Immunology, Microbiology and try to read neuroscience books as well.
🦁 When do you sleep and wake up? 21:00 - 5:10.
